parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, the horn to fail, and the cruise control to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or injuries in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates and remains on
and the radio controls may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy in a crash
and the vehicle may experience other electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries. It can also lead to expensive repairs and leave drivers stranded.
Clutch and hydraulic system failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries. It can also lead to expensive repairs and leave drivers stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling and power loss can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries. It can also lead to expensive repairs and leave drivers stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle engine dies out while driving
loss of power steering and brakes

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the serpentine belt can cause loss of power steering, overheating, and engine stall, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine sludge build-up can cause engine failure, leading to costly repairs and potential accidents.
Intermittent stalling and engine failure can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Timing belt and chain failure can cause engine damage and costly repairs.
The corrosion of brake lines can cause brake failure, leading to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle.

and rust or corrosion on brake lines.
